<p>The navigation bar pattern displays a horizontal navigation menu for the current section.</p>

<h3>Rules for the navigation bar</h3>

<ul>
    <li>This is required on all webpages.</li>
    <li>Should contain up to eight links.</li>
    <li>Must come below the category header and above the main body of the page.</li>
    <li>Must not contain dropdown menus.</li>
    <li>Must use the primary and secondary palette colours.</li>
</ul>

